{
  "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/diffie-hellman/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.73,
      "size": 43632,
      "text": "两个人从没见过面，聊天全程被人偷听，他们能约定一把只有彼此知道的钥匙吗？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/diffie-hellman/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "听起来不可能，但一九七六年的迪菲和赫尔曼做到了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/diffie-hellman/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "秘密不在于藏住对话，而在于藏住一个难以逆转的计算。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
      "section_id": "params",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "params-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/diffie-hellman/xiaoxiao/params-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "首先，双方公开约定一个素数 p，和它的一个原根 g。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
      "section_id": "params",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "params-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/diffie-hellman/xiaoxiao/params-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "这两个数写在明面上，全世界包括窃听者都能看到。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
      "section_id": "params",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "params-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/diffie-hellman/xiaoxiao/params-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.4,
      "size": 22464,
      "text": "真正的秘密，藏在各自心里的私钥里。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
      "section_id": "compute",
      "line_id": "cmp-1",
      "filename": "compute-cmp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/diffie-hellman/xiaoxiao/compute-cmp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "Alice 选私钥 a，算出公开值 A 等于 g 的 a 次方对 p 取模。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
      "section_id": "compute",
      "line_id": "cmp-2",
      "filename": "compute-cmp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/diffie-hellman/xiaoxiao/compute-cmp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "Bob 选私钥 b，同样算出 B 等于 g 的 b 次方对 p 取模。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
      "section_id": "compute",
      "line_id": "cmp-3",
      "filename": "compute-cmp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/diffie-hellman/xiaoxiao/compute-cmp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 28080,
      "text": "他们把 A 和 B 大大方方地在公开信道上交换。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
      "section_id": "shared",
      "line_id": "shr-1",
      "filename": "shared-shr-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/diffie-hellman/xiaoxiao/shared-shr-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "Alice 拿 B 再乘方 a 次，Bob 拿 A 再乘方 b 次。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
      "section_id": "shared",
      "line_id": "shr-2",
      "filename": "shared-shr-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/diffie-hellman/xiaoxiao/shared-shr-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.41,
      "size": 38592,
      "text": "奇妙的是，两边都等于 g 的 a 乘 b 次方对 p 取模，密钥完全相同。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
      "section_id": "shared",
      "line_id": "shr-3",
      "filename": "shared-shr-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/diffie-hellman/xiaoxiao/shared-shr-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "窃听者只有 A 和 B，想反推私钥要解离散对数，几乎不可能。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/diffie-hellman/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "试着给 Alice 和 Bob 各选一个私钥，看看两边的共享密钥。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/diffie-hellman/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "无论怎么换，只要参数不变，两边算出的密钥总是一致。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/diffie-hellman/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.78,
      "size": 28512,
      "text": "公开 p、g、A、B，私钥却始终不出门。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/diffie-hellman/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "快速幂让计算轻松，离散对数让破解无望。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "diffie-hellman",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/diffie-hellman/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.41,
      "size": 38592,
      "text": "这把在阳光下协商出的钥匙，撑起了今天的加密世界，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 34.64,
  "total_size": 554400
}